<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.5">
<l>pārāruṅ kāṇāmē paravaimā neṭuṅkaṭalē yāṉakālam</l>
<l>ārāṉu mavaṉuṭaiya tiruvayiṟṟil neṭuṅkālam kiṭantatuḷḷat</l>
<l>tōrāta vuṇarvilīru ṇarutirēlu lakaḷanta vumparkōmāṉ</l>
<l>pērāḷaṉ pērāṉa pērkaḷāyi raṅkaḷumē pēcīrkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without searching in [your] heart, you who do not understand</l>
<l rend="indent">everyone’s long-time repose in his divine stomach,</l>
<l>At the time when the great, vast sea became an expanse,</l>
<l rend="indent">without anyone seeing earth.</l>
<l>If you would understand [this], say only the one-thousand renowned names</l>
<l>Of the renowned one, the king of heaven who measured the world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
